data.title: Destroy All Monsters
data.meta_description: Destroy All Monsters (1968) starring Akira Kubo, Jun Tazaki, Yukiko Kobayashi and directed by Ishir Honda.
data.text: Aliens have released all of Earth's monsters from their imprisonment on Monsterland and are using them to destroy all of the major cities on the planet. It is up to the daring crew of the rocket ship Moonlight SY-3 to infiltrate the aliens' headquarters on the Moon before the Earth monsters and King Ghidorah annihilate the planet.
